definition: to get rid of/to remove/to exclude/to eliminate/to wipe out/to divide/except/not including

sentences.english: The current galvanizing mill will be removed and the six-high mill will be built in its place.
sentences.chinese: 目前鍍鋅廠將被刪除，將在其位置上興建的六輥軋機。

sentences.english: Remove 3 bolts holding headlamp in place.
sentences.chinese: 刪除3螺栓控股頭燈在的地方。

sentences.english: Do you really want to remove subproject %1 with all targets and files?
sentences.chinese: 您真要刪除子工程%1及所有目標和文件嗎？

sentences.english: We also intend to remove any special naming restriction.
sentences.chinese: 我們還希望刪除任何特殊的命名限制。

sentences.english: Any deletion or amendment must be initialed by all account holders.
sentences.chinese: 任何刪除或修改必須由客戶簽署作實。

sentences.english: The bread can be fresh or stale and crusts can be left on or removed.
sentences.chinese: 麪包可新鮮或陳舊的和結殼可以留在或刪除。

sentences.english: This is a visual effect that shows the picture disappearing to indicate that the picture has been deleted.
sentences.chinese: 這種視覺效果顯示照片消失的過程，表示已經刪除它。

sentences.english: Fill it with White andnudgeit down another 1px then press Delete.
sentences.chinese: 用白色填充再向下輕移1px然後刪除。

sentences.english: You should remove those ciphers or a client might select one of them.
sentences.chinese: 應該刪除這些密碼，否則客戶機可能會選用它們。

sentences.english: Do you really want to delete this initiator group?
sentences.chinese: 您確定要刪除這個創始者羣組嗎？

sentences.english: In a table-view row, to reveal the Delete button.
sentences.chinese: 在表視圖行，以顯示刪除按鈕。

sentences.english: Mechanisms for creating and removing breakpoints are provided by most debugging tools.
sentences.chinese: 大多數除錯工具提供增加與刪除一個斷點的機制。
此條評論一出，很快就被網管刪除。

sentences.english: Put details and digressions in footnotes. Then delete the footnotes.
sentences.chinese: 把細節和離題的東西放到腳註，然後刪除腳註。

sentences.english: Then removed from the clamp and opened at the back to apply the glue.
sentences.chinese: 然後刪除從夾具和後面開膠應用。

sentences.english: These objects represent data that needs to be removed from backend data structure.
sentences.chinese: 這些對象表示了需要從後端數據結構中刪除的數據。
